 The UI of the app consists of:
1. A navigation bar with a back button, a title "All Items", a search bar and an "Edit" button.
2. A sidebar with 5 items: Overview, Bills, Income, Reports and Archive.
3. A main view which shows a list of items. Each item has a name, an amount, a due date and a status. There is also a button "Log payment" and a button "Skip".
4. A button "View payment history" at the bottom of the main view.
5. A button "View statistics" at the bottom of the main view.
6. A button "Click to add notes" at the bottom of the main view.
7. An "Archive" button at the bottom right corner of the main view.